{"tid":341942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委內瑞拉修憲選舉衝突　過去24小時內13人被殺","createTime":"2017-07-31T08:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T08:57:54.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8953971626fe52f743f685c202cbba031c6621","tid":341942,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:16:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/108615/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E4%BF%AE%E6%86%B2%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB24%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%85%A713%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F108615%2F%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2591%259E%25E6%258B%2589%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%2586%25B2%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258E%25BB24%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2585%25A713%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AE%25BA&d=yX%2F66xiNI6rdAY%2FZDkS4L49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5c1f5352\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/108615/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E4%BF%AE%E6%86%B2%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB24%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%85%A713%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉周日（30日）舉行極富爭議的修憲選舉。政府與反對派發生衝突，一名候選人及一名反對派領袖被殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/737190/xlarge/b20c4d1e2d9723805a28fc4233f63de4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F737190%2Fxlarge%2Fb20c4d1e2d9723805a28fc4233f63de4.jpg&h=473dabb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者在路上堆積障礙物。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n該國總統馬杜羅（Nicolas Maduro）在5月召集「制憲會議」，負責起草新憲法。今次修憲選舉正是就此事投票，逾1900萬名合資格委內瑞拉選民，於6120名候選人中，選出545名會議代表，着手修憲工作。反對派指，這是馬杜羅企圖繞過由反對派聯盟控制的國會的技倆，擔憂委內瑞拉會變成獨裁統治的國家。但政府堅稱，此舉可解決當前政經危機，是讓該國回歸和平的唯一途徑。<br />\n<br />\n事發在投票開始前的周六（29日）晚上，當局指，39歲的候選人、律師妮達（Jos&eacute; Felix Pineda）在家被殺，頭部有槍傷。另外，反對派則指，民主行動黨的一名年輕書記甘布斯（Ricardo Campos）在周日（30日）的示威中被槍殺。當地傳媒更指，一名國民警衛士兵在示威中被殺。《國民報》（El Nacional）指，在過去24小時，至少有13人在委內瑞拉境內被殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/737189/xlarge/6d11e5b1c8f1065f0f1f30be13262ba4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F737189%2Fxlarge%2F6d11e5b1c8f1065f0f1f30be13262ba4.jpg&h=4357d4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防員正嘗試撲滅警局的火頭。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n雖然當局較早前已宣布，7月28日至8月1日期間禁止一切示威抗議，但示威者無視禁令。該國首都卡拉卡斯（Caracas）一個示威現場附近發生爆炸，多輛電單車起火，造成多名警員受傷。法新社引述消息指，當局用裝甲車驅趕卡拉卡斯街頭的示威者，期間有槍聲傳出。<br />\n<br />\n（BBC）"},{"pid":"9a0ab02cfde3d6e26dee7c26cc7f124195b7b182","tid":341942,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"將委內瑞拉變古巴: 查韋斯十幾年想做做唔到嘅野<br />\n而家終於實現到 (唔爆發內戰 / 美國唔介入嘅話)"},{"pid":"d96d49c4c73f851f8b9e567a450cead8e2c0339c","tid":341942,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"戴妖又話和理非非既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988b7c6c5798192756507af9d03481ec7e6da540","tid":341942,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戴妖又話和理非非既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢訓左四個月?"},{"pid":"f6f9d4085bce06e823f0c4153a43a724b959ac66","tid":341942,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"又想夾硬嚟通過"},{"pid":"18034b5ed385801ca072606e5f2a0dd24ebff0ca","tid":341942,"uid":117556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又想夾硬嚟通過</blockquote><br />\n獨裁者"},{"pid":"d5532ac12d36606dc275ea7302f53b50f6e0f662","tid":341942,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"cy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe66873ca7c34cfdf912a63894d0045d0ea7e06","tid":341942,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"香港人：唔好搞事啦 聽日要返工返學"},{"pid":"31f35696456099f0529e1272cbbd86ae2e84a548","tid":341942,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人：唔好搞事啦 聽日要返工返學</blockquote><br />\n人地都想返工,不過冇工返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6272053d4d6bae56e40956cce0131b801b5f23d2","tid":341942,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8bbd5c1eb1c5724c363f9c526081f26fc92efef","tid":341942,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"勁過之前果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}